279
00:19:52,440 --> 00:19:55,240
Your Wangquan Manor only has the Wangquan Sword,

280
00:19:55,350 --> 00:19:59,070
but our Nangong family has many demon swords.

281
00:19:59,680 --> 00:20:01,610
As long as demons don't go extinct,

282
00:20:01,720 --> 00:20:03,920
there will always be more in the future.

283
00:20:06,920 --> 00:20:09,220
My son is rough with his words,

284
00:20:09,590 --> 00:20:11,520
but he makes a point.

285
00:20:11,880 --> 00:20:14,590
Master Nangong, what do you mean?

286
00:20:18,720 --> 00:20:20,980
With the help of Dongfang Divine Fire,

287
00:20:21,580 --> 00:20:24,950
I will certainly be even stronger.

288
00:20:28,420 --> 00:20:30,820
I also have a Celestial Demon Divine Sword.

289
00:20:31,020 --> 00:20:33,820
I would like to invite you all to examine the sword!

290
00:21:27,390 --> 00:21:28,680
[Auspiciousness and Blessings]

291
00:21:34,820 --> 00:21:37,620
Raise the banner and challenge the Alliance Leader.

292
00:21:37,620 --> 00:21:40,010
Master Nangong Ye, is this what you mean?

293
00:21:40,440 --> 00:21:41,240
Indeed.

294
00:21:42,110 --> 00:21:44,590
Then you should take your Nangong family's banner

295
00:21:44,590 --> 00:21:45,960
and challenge the headquarters of the Yiqi Alliance,

296
00:21:45,960 --> 00:21:47,420
Wangquan Manor.

297
00:22:09,200 --> 00:22:12,590
When raising the banner and challenging the Alliance Leader,

298
00:22:12,590 --> 00:22:13,920
killing is acceptable.

299
00:22:14,590 --> 00:22:16,900
This is a rule set by the Yiqi Alliance.

300
00:22:17,720 --> 00:22:20,340
Since I want to change the rules,

301
00:22:20,750 --> 00:22:22,750
why do I have to stick to the old ways?

302
00:22:22,830 --> 00:22:24,620
The headquarters of Yiqi Alliance

303
00:22:24,620 --> 00:22:27,080
could also be my Nangong's residence.

304
00:22:28,070 --> 00:22:29,280
Family masters,

305
00:22:29,510 --> 00:22:30,590
what do you think?

306
00:22:45,960 --> 00:22:47,870
Today, I, Nangong Ye,

307
00:22:48,240 --> 00:22:49,790
raise my sword

308
00:22:50,070 --> 00:22:53,800
to challenge Wangquan Hongye for the position of Alliance Leader.

309
00:22:54,160 --> 00:22:57,090
This battle will be perilous and life-threatening.

310
00:22:57,350 --> 00:22:58,680
Young Master Wangquan,

311
00:22:59,640 --> 00:23:01,590
do you dare to accept the challenge?

312
00:23:01,590 --> 00:23:02,860
If you dare not,

313
00:23:03,030 --> 00:23:04,830
sever the Wangquan Sword first!

314
00:23:34,310 --> 00:23:35,640
After leaving the seat,

315
00:23:36,110 --> 00:23:37,710
take five steps, turn right,

316
00:23:38,050 --> 00:23:39,300
and then take

317
00:23:39,720 --> 00:23:40,780
ten steps forward.

318
00:24:03,510 --> 00:24:04,840
Young Master Wangquan,

319
00:24:05,720 --> 00:24:07,320
do you have to be so arrogant?

320
00:24:55,510 --> 00:24:57,920
If you want to challenge the Wangquan Sword,

321
00:24:57,920 --> 00:24:58,920
it depends on

322
00:24:59,550 --> 00:25:01,720
whether you have the ability.

323
00:25:29,200 --> 00:25:31,460
The Wangquan Sword isn't that powerful.

324
00:25:31,470 --> 00:25:32,900
The Yiqi Alliance

325
00:25:33,550 --> 00:25:35,480
will belong to the Nangong family.

326
00:25:36,350 --> 00:25:39,110
Young Master Wangquan, swords are ruthless.

327
00:25:39,240 --> 00:25:40,640
You still have time to admit defeat

328
00:25:40,640 --> 00:25:42,510
and sever the Wangquan Sword.

329
00:26:11,190 --> 00:26:12,410
All swords

330
00:26:15,350 --> 00:26:16,230
unite as one!

331
00:26:31,720 --> 00:26:34,000
What is the meaning of the Wangquan Sword?

332
00:26:34,000 --> 00:26:36,350
When the sword is drawn, all swords obey.

333
00:26:36,600 --> 00:26:38,730
Want to challenge the Wangquan Sword?

334
00:26:38,810 --> 00:26:39,880
Nangong Ye,

335
00:26:40,330 --> 00:26:41,460
do you deserve it?

336
00:26:49,040 --> 00:26:50,170
It was you.

337
00:26:51,030 --> 00:26:53,830
You broke the formation and saved him!

338
00:27:04,440 --> 00:27:06,960
Your only opponent is me.

339
00:27:08,190 --> 00:27:09,640
Ten years ago,

340
00:27:10,530 --> 00:27:12,830
I lost to Wangquan Shouzhuo

341
00:27:13,640 --> 00:27:16,610
because I wasn't ruthless enough.

342
00:27:17,790 --> 00:27:19,210
Today,

343
00:27:19,590 --> 00:27:22,910
I won't lose to this little boy!

344
00:27:30,530 --> 00:27:31,660
Something's wrong.

345
00:27:33,510 --> 00:27:35,000
I am...

346
00:27:35,730 --> 00:27:38,170
the strongest in the world!

347
00:27:48,690 --> 00:27:50,090
None of you...

348
00:27:50,590 --> 00:27:53,020
can stop me!

349
00:28:00,240 --> 00:28:00,920
Father!

350
00:28:03,320 --> 00:28:05,590
He's gone mad! He even killed his own son!

351
00:28:06,300 --> 00:28:08,350
Using demon cores to forge swords can really cause backfires!

352
00:28:08,350 --> 00:28:09,410
Let's go! Let's go!

353
00:28:27,030 --> 00:28:28,060
Wangquan Hongye!

354
00:28:28,110 --> 00:28:28,900
Enough!

355
00:29:16,110 --> 00:29:18,640
Miss Xie, use the Divine Fire to set them free.

356
00:29:38,680 --> 00:29:40,510
Forsaking emotions, pursuing hatred;

357
00:29:40,510 --> 00:29:42,260
eternal night befalls.

358
00:29:42,550 --> 00:29:45,710
None of you can escape.

359
00:29:46,590 --> 00:29:48,240
Forsaking emotions, pursuing hatred;

360
00:29:48,240 --> 00:29:49,940
eternal night befalls.

361
00:29:50,800 --> 00:29:51,870
Hongye,

362
00:29:52,320 --> 00:29:53,850
you must remember my words.

363
00:29:54,160 --> 00:29:56,340
Stop the conflict between humans and demons

364
00:29:56,340 --> 00:29:58,940
and prevent the eternal night from befalling.

365
00:30:07,590 --> 00:30:11,980
[Auspiciousness and Blessings]

366
00:30:25,590 --> 00:30:26,680
Congratulations, Young Master,

367
00:30:26,030 --> 00:30:27,740
[Sword Attendant Feng]

368
00:30:26,790 --> 00:30:28,250
for fulfilling your wish.

369
00:30:28,510 --> 00:30:29,640
I'll leave

370
00:30:30,400 --> 00:30:31,260
the rest to you.

371
00:30:31,680 --> 00:30:32,310
Yes.

372
00:31:24,620 --> 00:31:25,740
Young Master Wangquan.

373
00:31:25,740 --> 00:31:26,930
Miss Huaizhu,

374
00:31:27,590 --> 00:31:29,780
I called you here to inform you

375
00:31:29,860 --> 00:31:31,390
that Nan has been rescued.

376
00:31:31,680 --> 00:31:34,000
Yitan and Zui have already taken Nan to Tushan.

377
00:31:34,000 --> 00:31:35,350
There's a demon market

378
00:31:35,350 --> 00:31:37,200
that shelters homeless demons.

379
00:31:37,840 --> 00:31:39,070
If that is the case,

380
00:31:39,410 --> 00:31:41,270
I, Dongfang Huaizhu, would like to thank you

381
00:31:41,270 --> 00:31:43,270
on behalf of Nan and the other demons

382
00:31:43,330 --> 00:31:44,590
who have been saved.

383
00:31:47,810 --> 00:31:49,290
In a single day,

384
00:31:49,320 --> 00:31:52,000
you wiped out the Nangong noble family without leaving a trace.

385
00:31:52,000 --> 00:31:54,530
You are truly a remarkable person, capable of

386
00:31:54,540 --> 00:31:56,200
turning the tides of fate with a single motion.

387
00:31:56,200 --> 00:31:57,760
Are you insinuating

388
00:31:59,160 --> 00:32:00,690
that I am not a good person?

389
00:32:01,200 --> 00:32:02,310
Someone like you,

390
00:32:02,310 --> 00:32:04,310
standing at the center of the storm,

391
00:32:04,680 --> 00:32:07,010
cannot be described simply as good or bad.

392
00:32:09,070 --> 00:32:10,070
I see.

393
00:32:10,780 --> 00:32:11,970
What you mean is that

394
00:32:13,640 --> 00:32:15,500
we are not the same kind of people.

395
00:32:16,830 --> 00:32:19,490
What do you think about the words Nangong Ye said

396
00:32:19,920 --> 00:32:21,110
before his death?

397
00:32:26,550 --> 00:32:27,350
Young Master.

398
00:32:31,970 --> 00:32:33,410
[Young Master, Mu Xiaowu, the person you had me investigate, was arrested]

399
00:32:31,970 --> 00:32:33,410
[by the Inspection Bureau days ago on charges of unlawfully releasing demon slaves and is currently detained in their prison.]

400
00:32:33,690 --> 00:32:35,350
The person you're looking for

401
00:32:36,710 --> 00:32:38,710
is indeed in the Inspection Bureau.

402
00:32:41,930 --> 00:32:43,850
[Yiqi Alliance]
[Inspection Bureau]

403
00:32:51,110 --> 00:32:53,880
The Inspection Bureau is independent from the Yiqi Alliance.

404
00:32:53,880 --> 00:32:56,020
Are you planning to go there alone

405
00:32:56,040 --> 00:32:57,480
to rescue him?

406
00:32:58,880 --> 00:32:59,550
Let's go.

407
00:33:40,850 --> 00:33:41,940
Bring someone out?

408
00:33:42,110 --> 00:33:43,160
Who?

409
00:33:43,920 --> 00:33:44,880
Mu Xiaowu.

410
00:33:45,590 --> 00:33:48,520
This is the release document from the Yiqi Alliance.

411
00:33:49,240 --> 00:33:50,570
Who is Mu Xiaowu?

412
00:33:50,750 --> 00:33:52,460
His real name is Mu Renzhi.

413
00:33:52,790 --> 00:33:55,250
[Yiqi Alliance]
[Director of Inspection Bureau]

414
00:33:52,960 --> 00:33:54,890
He is the fifth-born in his family,

415
00:33:55,020 --> 00:33:56,950
so everyone calls him Mu Xiaowu.

416
00:34:00,270 --> 00:34:01,820
So what if there's a document?

417
00:34:01,820 --> 00:34:02,590
Even with a document,

418
00:34:02,590 --> 00:34:05,000
you still have to follow the rules of the Inspection Bureau.

419
00:34:05,000 --> 00:34:06,440
Let's calculate.

420
00:34:10,150 --> 00:34:11,150
Is this person male or female?

421
00:34:11,150 --> 00:34:12,440
How long have they been here?

422
00:34:12,440 --> 00:34:13,230
Male.

423
00:34:13,550 --> 00:34:15,320
He has probably been here for less than half a month.

424
00:34:15,320 --> 00:34:16,270
A male

425
00:34:18,000 --> 00:34:19,730
means he is capable of working.

426
00:34:20,110 --> 00:34:21,110
Here,

427
00:34:21,110 --> 00:34:22,960
his starting price for release is 300 taels.

428
00:34:22,960 --> 00:34:24,900
His daily expenses are 2.2 taels.

429
00:34:25,510 --> 00:34:26,920
He has been here for 15 days.

430
00:34:26,920 --> 00:34:28,710
15 days is...

431
00:34:29,429 --> 00:34:30,560
3 multiplied by 5...

432
00:34:30,630 --> 00:34:33,810
Then, add an inspection fee.

433
00:34:34,230 --> 00:34:36,230
This, rounded off,

434
00:34:36,840 --> 00:34:38,719
comes to around 400 taels.

435
00:34:39,190 --> 00:34:41,150
After paying and completing the registration,

436
00:34:41,150 --> 00:34:42,360
you can bring him out in ten days.

437
00:34:42,360 --> 00:34:43,400
It costs money

438
00:34:43,630 --> 00:34:44,889
to be imprisoned here?

439
00:34:47,630 --> 00:34:48,550
What?

440
00:34:48,670 --> 00:34:51,190
Are you saying that eating, drinking, and other needs here don't cost money?

441
00:34:51,190 --> 00:34:53,880
Then why do we need to wait for 10 days to bring him out?

442
00:34:53,880 --> 00:34:54,630
Why?

443
00:34:55,110 --> 00:34:56,920
I have so many people imprisoned here.

444
00:34:56,920 --> 00:34:57,800
I need to release them one by one.

445
00:34:57,800 --> 00:34:58,800
Doesn't it need

446
00:34:58,800 --> 00:35:00,180
verification?

447
00:35:00,400 --> 00:35:02,030
What if I release the wrong person one day?

448
00:35:02,030 --> 00:35:03,710
Who's going to take responsibility

449
00:35:03,710 --> 00:35:05,160
for that, you or you?

450
00:35:05,880 --> 00:35:06,670
Cut the crap.

451
00:35:06,960 --> 00:35:08,290
Pay the money and leave.

452
00:35:08,510 --> 00:35:09,430
Miss Huaizhu,

453
00:35:10,440 --> 00:35:12,100
what do you think we should do?

454
00:35:13,440 --> 00:35:16,190
Young Master, I came in a rush

455
00:35:16,510 --> 00:35:18,280
and didn't bring that much money.

456
00:35:18,280 --> 00:35:19,320
Why don't we

457
00:35:19,400 --> 00:35:22,030
use your sword to offset the cost?

458
00:35:26,450 --> 00:35:27,440
Come on. What are you two

459
00:35:27,440 --> 00:35:28,630
whispering about?

460
00:35:29,880 --> 00:35:31,320
You think you can just use a stupid sword

461
00:35:31,320 --> 00:35:33,270
to offset 400 taels of silver?

462
00:35:33,510 --> 00:35:35,110
Do you think your sword is...

463
00:35:38,710 --> 00:35:39,640
The wangquan...

464
00:35:41,530 --> 00:35:42,660
The Wangquan Sword?

465
00:35:43,440 --> 00:35:46,240
Young Master, aren't you at Nangong's residence?

466
00:35:47,400 --> 00:35:48,910
You're well-informed.

467
00:35:49,280 --> 00:35:51,900
Have you also placed your bets on Nangong Ye,

468
00:35:52,070 --> 00:35:53,510
hoping that the Yiqi Alliance

469
00:35:53,510 --> 00:35:56,880
will change its leader?

470
00:35:56,900 --> 00:35:57,820
I dare not.

471
00:36:05,140 --> 00:36:06,430
Within ten counts,

472
00:36:07,400 --> 00:36:08,660
I want to see Mu Xiaowu.

473
00:36:10,000 --> 00:36:10,880
Otherwise...

474
00:36:19,940 --> 00:36:21,900
[Mu Xiaowu]

475
00:36:21,550 --> 00:36:22,360
Yan.

476
00:36:24,590 --> 00:36:25,330
Yan!

477
00:36:26,760 --> 00:36:27,550
Xiaowu?

478
00:36:29,080 --> 00:36:29,630
How have you been?

479
00:36:29,630 --> 00:36:30,150
Yan!

480
00:36:33,080 --> 00:36:35,010
A couple eventually got together.

481
00:36:35,280 --> 00:36:36,980
It can be considered a good story.

482
00:36:36,980 --> 00:36:38,670
It's too early to say that.

483
00:36:41,370 --> 00:36:43,540
Yitan's grandfather is proud

484
00:36:43,630 --> 00:36:45,090
and values bloodlines greatly.

485
00:36:45,090 --> 00:36:46,980
Someone as ordinary as Mu Xiaowu

486
00:36:47,230 --> 00:36:48,830
is unlikely to catch his eye.

487
00:36:49,610 --> 00:36:51,140
Success depends on effort.

488
00:36:51,470 --> 00:36:54,220
Some things are worth fighting for.

489
00:36:57,040 --> 00:36:58,150
No matter what,

490
00:36:58,440 --> 00:37:00,280
I've brought out the person you mentioned.

491
00:37:00,280 --> 00:37:02,510
Now, can you cure me of the poison?

492
00:37:04,240 --> 00:37:05,910
Young Master, please don't rush.

493
00:37:05,910 --> 00:37:06,460
Really?

494
00:37:07,620 --> 00:37:08,510
Really?

495
00:37:09,030 --> 00:37:09,800
Yes.

496
00:37:10,220 --> 00:37:11,520
That's great, Yan!

497
00:37:11,550 --> 00:37:12,230
Be careful!

498
00:37:12,290 --> 00:37:14,070
Yan, we are having a child, Yan!

499
00:37:14,230 --> 00:37:15,400
Are we really having a child?

500
00:37:15,400 --> 00:37:16,530
Be careful.

501
00:37:17,150 --> 00:37:18,660
Just as you said,

502
00:37:19,430 --> 00:37:22,840
I don't think that just because Yan is pregnant,

503
00:37:23,000 --> 00:37:25,150
Mu Xiaowu, coming from a poor family,

504
00:37:25,230 --> 00:37:26,500
would be accepted by the Yang family.

505
00:37:26,500 --> 00:37:28,030
That's great, Yan!

506
00:37:30,050 --> 00:37:31,070
Put me down.

507
00:37:32,230 --> 00:37:33,440
Don't tell me

508
00:37:33,760 --> 00:37:37,020
you want me to personally act as a matchmaker for Mu Xiaowu.

509
00:37:37,550 --> 00:37:39,440
Yes. I hope you can help.

510
00:37:40,960 --> 00:37:42,630
How far should I go?

511
00:37:42,820 --> 00:37:45,800
I can't be looking after them for their whole lives, can I?

512
00:37:45,800 --> 00:37:47,600
Within a month would be the best.

513
00:37:47,670 --> 00:37:49,070
Once they are married,

514
00:37:49,340 --> 00:37:50,690
I will cure your poison.

515
00:37:50,960 --> 00:37:52,030
A month? That soon?

516
00:37:52,670 --> 00:37:54,020
The longer we wait, the more troubles will occur.

517
00:37:54,020 --> 00:37:56,580
I owe you this one.

518
00:38:00,860 --> 00:38:02,230
This friend

519
00:38:04,200 --> 00:38:05,460
is so important to you?

520
00:38:06,540 --> 00:38:09,370
How fortunate in life it is to have a confidant.

521
00:38:10,060 --> 00:38:11,640
Yan is

522
00:38:11,800 --> 00:38:13,520
a part of my life to me.

523
00:38:15,890 --> 00:38:16,940
Miss Huaizhu,

524
00:38:29,260 --> 00:38:30,790
go back and wait for my news.

525
00:38:31,760 --> 00:38:33,890
Then I'll be waiting for the good news.

526
00:38:34,350 --> 00:38:35,750
Young Master, take care.

527
00:39:05,730 --> 00:39:06,610
Your Highness.

528
00:39:07,990 --> 00:39:09,190
As you expected,

529
00:39:09,590 --> 00:39:11,540
the conflict between humans and demons within the circle never ends,

530
00:39:11,540 --> 00:39:13,230
with hatred growing stronger.

531
00:39:13,230 --> 00:39:15,930
You will become more and more powerful.

532
00:39:16,320 --> 00:39:17,370
Not enough.

533
00:39:17,800 --> 00:39:18,810
It's not enough.

534
00:39:19,890 --> 00:39:21,030
I don't care about

535
00:39:21,500 --> 00:39:22,720
humans or demons.

536
00:39:23,270 --> 00:39:25,590
I want this world to be in ruins.

537
00:39:25,800 --> 00:39:27,270
Hatred and despair

538
00:39:27,640 --> 00:39:29,740
are the sources of my power.

539
00:39:38,940 --> 00:39:41,740
With love fading and hatred growing in this world,

540
00:39:42,740 --> 00:39:44,940
I will definitely return to the circle.

541
00:39:47,790 --> 00:39:48,950
Darkness

542
00:39:49,070 --> 00:39:51,240
will consume everything!
